{
  "stem": "33.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But they were not used.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were not eaten from the same dishes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was, you know, eaten off paper or paper plates.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My father believed in a independent state for Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He wasn't a active Zionist, but he considered that as the solution to Jewish problem.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he was a Jew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I guess for him, like for me, being Jewish is more a state of mind than a religion.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But he was not religious at all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He-- they did go to Temple on high holidays, but only because my mother insisted on it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "My father probably wouldn't have even done that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I think in real traditional Jewish families, that feeling of inferiority wasn't as frequent as in families like mine, where we were assimilated, and we wanted to be like everybody else.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we couldn't, because we were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My happy childhood sort of ended in 1940 for a while.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because in 1940, northern Transylvania was attached to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Hungary was a very faithful ally of Nazi Germany.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And a lot of the territories that were taken away after first world war were given back to Hungary in the '40s, starting in 1938.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We-- our turn came in-- on September 5th of 1940.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One of the anti-Jewish laws that affected me directly was that Jewish children were not admitted to high schools.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was a ceiling of 6%.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it was entirely up to the administration of the high school whether they wanted any Jews or not.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "As it happened in the Catholic school that-- where I went to, they decided that we-- excuse me-- that they will only take one in the upper classes, starting with ninth grade.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the one that they took was one of my best friends.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
